longBusinessSummary: Waaree Renewable Technologies Limited engages in the generation of power through renewable energy sources in India. The company offers ground mounted solar; solar capex model; resco opex; rooftop solar; floating solar; and operations and maintenance solutions; as well as generates electricity from solar power plants. It also provides engineering, procurement, and construction (EPC) services. The company serves the individual, industrial, and commercial sectors. Waaree Renewable Technologies Limited was formerly known as Sangam Renewables Limited and changed its name to Waaree Renewable Technologies Limited in July 2021. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India. Waaree Renewable Technologies Limited operates as a subsidiary of Waaree Energies Limited.
